Package: promptmanageR
Type: Package
Title: Manage and Reuse Prompts for LLM and AI Clients in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
  c(person("Lazaro", "Alvarez", email = "lazarusalvarez3@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: A lightweight R package for managing reusable system and user prompts 
  stored in JSON files. Provides utilities for creating, loading, and 
  rendering prompt templates that can be easily integrated into ellmer, Shiny, 
  or other programmatic workflows. Includes helper functions to bootstrap and 
  register prompt files in .Rprofile for automatic discovery.
